Package schedulemanager.domain

package schedulemanager.domain
Domain model classes representing core business entities.

Contains the data structures used throughout the application:

  • Task - A task with title, status, priority
  • TaskFolder - Hierarchical folder for organizing tasks
  • TodayTask - Task selected for a specific day
  • PlanBlock - Planned time block on the calendar
  • ActualSession - Recorded work session
  • DailyStatistics - Planned vs actual statistics

Enumerations:

  • TaskStatus - TODO, DOING, DONE
  • Priority - LOW, MEDIUM, HIGH, URGENT
